{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cbce5ac557","title":"给毛远梯的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"47635e6e21","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":12,"articleId":"cbce5ac557"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"fcb660ad87","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛远梯，1924年生，湖南省韶山市韶山乡韶源村人，毛泽东的房径。1945年加入中国共产党，从事过工人运动、学生运动等方面的工作。新中国成立后，曾任湖南省总工会工农印刷厂经理、湖南省医药管理局办公室主任等职。"},{"id":"ba8bd04e15","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"远翔，即毛远翔。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f8dc502fb5","type":"title","text":"给毛远梯的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557"},{"id":"fcb660ad87","type":"paragraph","text":"远梯贤径：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557"},{"id":"ba8bd04e15","type":"paragraph","text":"两次来信都收到了，很高兴。你做印广工作极好，应将此项工作做好，不要来北京。学习事将来有机会时再说。远翔是否尚在革大，有一信请转交。远翔历我忘记了，便时请告我。此祝进步！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557"},{"id":"8a5431092d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557"},{"id":"a5d3c579bf","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年五月十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557"}],"page":{"id":"032a1e2832","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"cbce5ac557","start":382,"end":382}}}},"__N_SSG":true}